==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From G1225; a traducer; specifically Satan (compare [H7854]): 

===Pronunciation===
*[[διάβολος]] / diabolos / dee-ab'-ol-os

===Noun===
'''διάβολος'''

# false accuser, [[devil]], slanderer.

